Requirements
   *rvm  
   *Ruby
   *Rails 3.1
   *Mysql

Implementation Stapes
   1) git clone
   2) cd dependent_dropdown  #open the directory
   3) change mysql password in config/database.yml  # mysql password
   4) rake db:create         # creation of database
   5) rake db:migrate        # execute the migration
   6) bundle install         # for downloading gem files
   6) rails s                # for running server
   7) open browser and put url "http://0.0.0.0:3000"

   